channel.description: Add a third-party risk provider Click here to give feedback about this page Content Notes Target personas: WIC App Developer,Experienced IAM developer Description: This document shows how to configure a third party provider using the API and create a simple event log. I think we could make this use case more robust and describe a better more detailed use case. This risk engine described in this doc can be useful in both secure and system log.
